To install Terraform on a windows machine:-

Step 1 - Open powershell
Step 2 - Download the .exe file for the windows machine from the terraform official website Link-https://developer.hashicorp.com/terraform/downloads?product_intent=terraform
Step 3 - Download the Zip file 
Step 4 - Open the powershell terminal on windows 
Step 5 -C:\> MKDIR terraform
        C:\> CD terraform
Step 6 - unzip the file and paste it to the terraform folder
Step 7 - install Chocolatey: Set-ExecutionPolicy Bypass -Scope Process -Force; [System.Net.ServicePointManager]::SecurityProtocol = [System.Net.ServicePointManager]::SecurityProtocol -bor 3072; iex ((New-Object System.Net.WebClient).DownloadString('https://community.chocolatey.org/install.ps1'))
Step 8 - choco install terraform
Step 9 - terraform version  
